.
 It is the sum of scalar multiples of matrices.
 More generally, if 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 is any set of objects on which addition and scalar mutliplication are defined
 (sound familiar?), 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1},c_{2},\ldots,c_{n}$
\end_inset

