\begin_inset Formula $b_{1},b_{2},\ldots,b_{n}$
\end_inset

 are in 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, then the expression 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
c_{1}b_{1}+c_{2}b_{2}+\cdots+c_{n}b_{n}
\]

\end_inset

is called a linear combination of the objects 
\begin_inset Formula $b_{1},b_{2},\ldots,b_{n}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1},c_{2},\ldots,c_{n}$
\end_inset

 are called the 
\series bold
